Class Graph

  • java.lang.Object
    • hw5.Graph

  • public class Graph
extends Object
    This class represents a graph which is made up of nodes and edges which connect these nodes. Specification fields:
    Specification Fields:
    graph - : Map // Maps the nodes in the graph to the edges they are contained in. Abstract Invariant: A graph cannot contain identical nodes. An edge in the graph may only only contain one instance of a parent node pointing to a child node. A edge may 'self-reference', where it starts and ends on the same node.
